methods.getPageSize:
The number of bytes in a memory page

:return: (long) Page size in bytes.
methods.getPhysicalTotal:
The amount of actual physical memory, in bytes.

:return: (long) Total number of bytes.
methods.getSwapTotal:
The current size of the paging/swap file(s), in bytes. If the paging/swap file can be extended, this is a soft
 limit.

:return: (long) Total swap in bytes.
methods.traverse:
Traverse this property set and output the property key/values to the given visitor.
 
 Callers should typically prefer to call PropertyVisitor.visitProperties(PropertySet), as the inversion of
 logic allows the visitor (the more stateful object) to potentially perform initialization logic and traverse more
 efficiently.

:param visitor: (io.deephaven.properties.PropertyVisitor) - the visitor
